                                   \"traces/\"\r\n                                      ],\r\n                      \"requirement_ids\":  [\r\n                                              \"FR-001\",\r\n                                              \"FR-002\",\r\n                                              \"FR-003\",\r\n                                              \"FR-004\",\r\n                                              \"FR-005\",\r\n                                              \"FR-006\",\r\n                                              \"FR-007\",\r\n                                              \"FR-008\",\r\n                                              \"FR-009\",\r\n                                              \"FR-010\",\r\n                                              \"FR-011\",\r\n                                              \"FR-012\",\r\n                                              \"FR-013\",\r\n                                              \"FR-014\"\r\n                                          ],\r\n                      \"produces_artifacts\":  [\r\n                                                 \"docs/testing/verify-matrix.md\",\r\n                                                 \"traces/\"\r\n                                             ],\r\n                      \"execution\":  {\r\n                                        \"mode\":  \"single\"\r\n                                    },\r\n                      \"steps\":  [\r\n                                    \"确认外部哨兵依赖 REAL-RELEASE-ENV-READY 已由人工解除阻塞：真实 MySQL EXPORT_PLATFORM_TEST_DATABASE_URL 与 live object storage endpoint、bucket、credential、EXPORT_PLATFORM_OBJECT_STORAGE_ALLOW_SMOKE_WRITES=true 均已配置完成并确认可用于 release gate\",\r\n                                    \"运行 release 所需的架构检查、契约测试、API 集成测试、DB/worker 测试和 P0/P1 回归\",\r\n                                    \"核对所有 evidence 是否来自 fresh-start 后的新实现，不引用旧内存实现或旧 trace\",\r\n                                    \"记录通过证据、失败归因、BLOCKED