 3060) has been terminated.\r\nSUCCESS: The process with PID 3060 (child process of PID 29036) has been terminated.\r\nSUCCESS: The process with PID 29036 (child process of PID 15992) has been terminated.\r\nSUCCESS: The process with PID 15992 (child process of PID 5280) has been terminated.\r\nSUCCESS: The process with PID 5280 (child process of PID 5844) has been terminated.\r\nSUCCESS: The process with PID 14876 (child process of PID 24100) has been terminated.\r\nSUCCESS: The process with PID 24100 (child process of PID 15932) has been terminated.\r\nSUCCESS: The process with PID 15932 (child process of PID 25828) has been terminated.\r\nSUCCESS: The process with PID 25828 (child process of PID 5844) has been terminated.\r\nBLOCKED - 需要人工介入\n\n当前任务: `LOCAL-RELEASE-REHEARSAL-001` 执行本地 release rehearsal，使用本地 MySQL 与本地 object storage mock 先压通 API、DB、worker、query、file 和 sample 集成链路\n\n已完成的工作:\n- `npm run release:local-rehearsal` 默认携带 `-StartLocalObjectStorageMock`。\n- `scripts/local-release-rehearsal.ps1` 增加无 object storage endpoint 时自动启本地 mock 的兜底。\n- 文档同步声明 rehearsal 只能是 `mock/local rehearsal evidence`，不能替代 `RELEASE-001`、真实 MySQL、live object storage 或正式 release evidence。\n- 未修改 `task.json`、`progress.txt`、`traces/`；未执行 commit，因为本任务模板明确禁止 `git add` / `git commit`。\n\n阻塞原因:\n- 当前环境缺少 `EXPORT_PLATFORM_TEST_DATABASE_URL`。\n- `npm run release:local-rehearsal` 已执行，按预期在本地 MySQL gate 输出 `BLOCKED - 需要人工介入`，未伪造通过。\n\n需要人工操作:\n1. 设置可用的本地 MySQL URL：`EXPORT_PLATFORM_TEST_DATABASE_URL`。\n2. 重新运行 `npm run release:local-rehearsal`。\n\n解除阻塞后请运行:\n```powershell\npowershell -NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File .\\codex-loop.ps1\n```\n\n## Requirement IDs\n- FR-001 至 FR-014\n\n## Summary\n- 本地 rehearsal 入口已默认启动 object storage mock。\n- rehearsal 仍强制要求本地 MySQL，缺失时明确 BLOCKED。\n- release 边界已同步，`RELEASE-001` 和 `REAL-RELEASE-ENV-READY` 不被解除。\n\n## Files Changed\n- `package.json`: 更新 `release:local-rehearsal` 命令。\n- `scripts/local-release-rehearsal.ps1`: 增加默认启本地 mock 兜底。\n- `tests/mock-local/local-release-rehearsal-docs.test.mjs`: 固定命令与边界断言。\n- `docs/testing/mock-first-release-plan.md`: 同步 rehearsal 证据口径。\n- `docs/testing/verify-matrix.md`: 同步验证矩阵口径。\n\n## Validation\n- `npm run test:mock-local`: PASS - 15/15 passed\n- `npm test`: PASS - 17/17 passed\n- PowerShell parser check: PASS\n- `git diff --check -- package.json scripts/local-release-rehearsal.ps1 tests/mock-local/local-release-rehearsal-docs.test.mjs docs/testing/mock-first-release-plan.md docs/testing/verify-matrix.md`: PASS\n- `npm run release:local-rehearsal`: FAIL - BLOCKED，缺少 `EXPORT_PLATFORM_TEST_DATABASE_URL`\n\n## Evidence\n- `tests/mock-local/local-release-rehearsal-docs.test.mjs`: 证明 rehearsal 命令和 release 边界被测试锁定。\n- `docs/testing/mock-first-release-plan.md`: 证明 mock/local evidence 不替代 release。\n- `docs/testing/verify-matrix.md`: 证明验证矩阵保留正式 release blocker。\n\n## Architecture Constraints\n- `delivery_shape=independent_microservice`: PASS - 未改生产形态。\n- `mock/local rehearsal evidence only`: PASS - 文档和脚本输出均保留边界。\n- `forbidden_implementations`: PASS - 未引入 `InMemory*`、mock repository 或 fixture 到生产路径。\n\n## Knowledge References\n- none\n\n## Knowledge Outputs\n- `suggested-process-local-release-rehearsal-boundary`: process - 本地 rehearsal 默认 mock 但仍不替代 release evidence - suggested - `docs/knowledge/processes/`\n\n## Visual Evidence\n- reference: `none`\n- screenshot: `none`\n- parity report: `none`\n\n## Remaining Risks\n- 本机缺少本地 MySQL URL，API / DB / worker / query / file / sample 集成链路尚未压通。\n- 工作区存在未跟踪 trace 目录，我按任务边界未触碰。\n\nOpenAI Codex v0.130.0\n--------\nworkdir: E:\\2026\\alpha-project\\longgang-codex-driver\nmodel: gpt-5.5\nprovider: sub2api\napproval: never\nsandbox: danger-full-access\nreasoning effort: high\nreasoning summaries: none\nsession id: 019e29eb-8ad2-7b52-9984-f293267c2c47\n--------\nuser\n# Codex 单任务实现 Prompt 模板\n\n## 元信息\n\n- 版本: v2.0\n- 标签: codex, harness, implementation, non-interactive\n\n## 角色\n\n你是一个非交互 Codex 自动实现会话。你只处理 Driver Context 中指定的一个任务，不负责调度、提交、更新任务状态或评审其他任务。\n\n## 输入\n\nDriver 会在本模板后追加 `## Driver Context`，其中包含：\n\n- 当前任务 ID、描述、类型、阶段、优先级和依赖\n- task session 策略、truth source、context files、produces artifacts、architecture constraints、forbidden implementations\n- knowledge catalog、knowledge query budget 和归档约束（如任务声明）\n- 子代理策略\n- 执行步骤、验收标准和测试命令\n\n## 工作流程\n\n1. 先阅读 Driver Context。\n2. 只读取优先上下文源和任务相关文件；信息不足时再做最小范围扩展检索。\n3. 如果存在 `docs/knowledge/knowledge-catalog.md`，先按任务阶段判断是否需要读取 `docs/knowledge/catalog.md` 和相关条目；遵守 `knowledge_query_budget`，不要贪婪读取整库。\n4. 先确认 Architecture Constraints Packet：读取 `docs/architecture/constraints.md`（如存在）、任务的 `architecture_constraints` 和 `forbidden_implementations`；如果当前任务需要生产路径，不得用测试替身、内存实现或领域原型替代。\n5. 先确认当前任务对应的 Requirement IDs、验收示例、追溯矩阵和测试影响，再对照 Product / Design / Testing / Contract / DEV-PLAN / Knowledge 等 truth source 改文件。\n6. 如需使用子代理，先确定子代理角色，再先阅读 `AGENTS.md`、`docs/harness/task-session-strategy.md`、`.agents/rules/agents.md`、`docs/harness/knowledge-architecture.md`、对应 `.agents/skills/*/SKILL.md`（如存在）和必要的深文档，然后只传最小必要上下文给子代理。\n7. 如果相关测试不存在，先补测试骨架、测试计划或稳定选择器，再实现业务代码。\n8. 按任务步骤实现最小必要改动，并同步更新相关测试、证据路径或测试文档。\n9. 自检是否满足验收标准、测试影响、架构约束、知识引用和 forbidden path 约束。\n10. 在最终回答中给出 Requirement IDs、修改摘要、涉及文件、验证命令、证据路径、architecture constraints result、knowledge references、knowledge outputs 和剩余风险。\n\n## 强制边界\n\n- 不要处理 `task.json` 中其他任务。\n- 不要删除或改写任务描述。\n- 不要修改 `task.json`、`progress.txt`、`traces/`、`smoke-task.json`。\n- 不要修改 `trace.schema.json`，除非当前任务明确把它列入 owned paths 且任务目标就是 harness/runtime schema 改造。\n- 不要执行 `git add`、`git commit`、`git push`、`git reset`、`git checkout`。\n- 不要修改与当前任务无关的文件。\n- 不要在没有验收示例或追溯矩阵支撑时自行猜测 P0/P1 业务规则。\n- 不要在没有 `docs/architecture/constraints.md` 或等价架构约束说明时开始 `feature_impl`；如果任务缺少约束但明显涉及服务形态、数据持久化、外部接口或 worker，输出 BLOCKED。\n- 不要把 `InMemory*`、mock、fixture、local-only adapter 或纯领域原型作为生产实现完成，除非任务 `architecture_constraints` 明确声明 `delivery_shape=domain-prototype`。\n- 不要违反任务 `forbidden_implementations`；如发现当前任务验收与 forbidden implementation 冲突，输出 BLOCKED。\n- 如果子代理策略是 `off`，不要主动使用子代理。\n- 如果子代理策略不是 `off`，只